n_final_portrait.pdf |title=Submarine Delivery Agency Corporate Plan 2018-2019 |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=23 April 2018 |website=gov.uk |publisher=Submarine Delivery Agency |access-date=4 January 2020 |quote=The SDA is a new Executive Agency of the Ministry of Defence}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Chief Executive\n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n|  Ian Booth <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2017 - \n|}\n\n===Functions===\n====Directorate-General (Commercial)====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Director-General, Commercial\n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| Nick Elliot <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2015\n|}\n\n=====Commercial Improvements=====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Director Commercial Improvements \n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| Morag Stuart <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2017 - \n|}\n\n=====Commercial Operations=====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Director DE&S Commercial Operations   \n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| Alan Peter <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2017 -\n|-\n| Phil Tozer <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2017 -\n \n|}\n\n=====Commercial Capability=====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Director Commercial Capability   \n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n|Mike Greatwich <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2017 - \n|}\n\n=====Support=====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Commercial Support  \n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| Steve Glass <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2019 - \n|}\n\n=====Information Technology=====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Director Chief Information Officer \n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| Nigel Shaw <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2019  - Present\n|}\n\n====Directorate-General (Resources)====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Director-General, Resources\n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| Michael Bradley <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2016-2018\n|-\n| David Johnson <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2019-Present\n|}\n\n=====Finance=====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Director Financial Plans & Analysis  \n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| David Johnson <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2017 - 2019\n|-\n| Ann Underwood <ref name=\"auto2\