d]] \n| 1 September 2009<ref>London Gazette 59191 dated 22 September 2009</ref> to May 2012\n|-\n| Lieutenant General [[Christopher Deverell]]\n| May 2012 to 8 March 2016<ref>[http://www.defenceviewpoints.co.uk/defence-news/up-and-out-june-2011 Defence View points] June 2011</ref>\n|-\n| Lieutenant General [[Paul Jaques]] <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n|  8 March 2016 - 7 December 2019<ref>{{London Gazette |issue=62850 |date=10 December 2019 |page=22294  |supp=y}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=====Directorate of Land Equipment=====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Director Land Equipment\n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| Major-General Robert Talbot Rice <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2017 - 2017\n|-\n| Major-General Colin McClean<ref>{{London Gazette |issue=62082 |date=17 October 2017 |page=19198   |supp=y}}</ref> \n| 2017-2019\n|-\n| Major-General Daniel Crook <ref>{{London Gazette |issue=62864 |date=24 December 2019 |page=23312  |supp=y}}</ref>  \n| 2019-present\n|}\n\n=====Directorate of Weapons=====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Director Weapons\n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| Richard Smart <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| 2017 - \n|}\n\n====Chief of Materiel (Air)====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Chief of Materiel (Air)\n|-\n! Name\n! Date held\n|-\n| Air-Marshal [[Barry Thornton|Sir Barry Thornton]]<ref name=\"Defence Equipment & Support - April 2007\"/>\n| 1 April 2007 - 30 April 2009\n|-\n| Air-Marshal [[Kevin Leeson|Sir Kevin Leeson]] \n| 1 May 2009<ref>[http://www.raf.mod.uk/rafcms/mediafiles/A9BE83B8_1143_EC82_2E216ECCD78F25C0.doc Royal Air Force Air Rank Appointments List 08/09] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090418001541/http://www.raf.mod.uk/rafcms/mediafiles/A9BE83B8_1143_EC82_2E216ECCD78F25C0.doc |date=2009-04-18 }} retrieved 17 November 2008</ref> \u2013 October 2012\n|-\n| Air-Marshal [[Simon Bollom]] \n| October 2012 \u2013 April 2016\n|-\n| Air-Marshal [[Julian Young (RAF officer)|Julian Young]] <ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n| April 2016 \u2013\n|}\n\n=====Directorate of Air Support===